Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&AB9E9A}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&000000\4c&000000}可以稍微抱一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&AB9E9A}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&000000\4c&000000}少しだけぎゅーってしてもいいですか
