Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&D9CAC5\bord2\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}もう好きにしていいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&D9CAC5\bord2\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}随我便
