Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.41,Dial-CHI,,333,0,0,,{\c&ADA19C}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&000000\4c&000000}诶 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.41,Dial-JPN,,333,0,0,,{\c&ADA19C}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&000000\4c&000000}え　何
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ADA19C}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&000000\4c&000000}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.12,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ADA19C}{\bord2\blur0.7\3c&000000\4c&000000}ちょっと
