Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:46.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&A8978F\bord1.5\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}ずいぶんとゆがんだ認識だ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&A8978F\bord1.5\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}我们明明拥有语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&A8978F\bord1.5\blur0.7\3c&0D0D0D\4c&0D0D0D}我らには言葉があるというのに
