Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.94,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\blur2}誰もがこの星の子孫
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.86,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\blur2}含着那份 珍藏的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.86,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\blur2}約束はね　大事にね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}让它融化在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.98,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}温かく残ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.73,0:01:29.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2\pos(1920,1688.8)}让它融化在心底
